SHOOT IN SPACE
---------------------------
World
	Screen Size 1024x768

	
SpaceObject
	Accelerate forward
	Physics object	
	Bounces off screen edges
	Take damage
	Explode when zero life
	
Player : SpaceObject	
	Rotate 360 towards mouse
	Accelerate forward on right click
	Deceleare with time
	Fire laser shots forward with left click
	Collide with enemies
	
Asteroid : SpaceObject
	Physics object
	Randomly created of screen with velocity towards a point in side game area.
	Takes damage from collision or laser shots

Big  Asteroid : Asteroid
	Explodes into small asteroids when destroyed
	
Small Asteroid : Asteroid
	Explodes and dissaperas when destroyed
	
	